#FragileX was the 1st trinucleotide repeat disorder described.  CGG
The macroorchidism of #FragileX doesn't show up until puberty. Dr T says we should remember this.
The premutation of #FragileX increases in size when transmitted by mothers,  but doesn't change when transmitted by fathers.
#FragileX Tremor Ataxia Syndrome -  one of the other phenotypes of the FMR1 mutation - is often misdiagnosed as Alzheimers.
Two percent.  That's the prevalence of #FragileX associated premature ovarian failure among ovarian failure patients.
Order PCR for #FragileX in boys & girls with dev delay, autism, or intellectual disability.  If repeats are < 45, the test is normal.
